---
description: FIELD-O Firebase and local data rules
globs:
  - "src/**/*"
alwaysApply: true
---

FIELD-O uses a hybrid data model:
- local drafts in IndexedDB / Dexie
- cloud persistence in Firestore
- future image storage in Firebase Storage

Rules:
- preserve offline-first behavior
- keep sync states explicit
- do not assume connectivity is always available
- maintain clear separation between local draft data and synced cloud data
- all client and report entities must remain strongly typed
- future auth should be easy to reintroduce

When changing data structures, update docs/tech/DATA_MODEL.md.

